criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Previously hospitalized for SARS-CoV-2 infection;

          -  Pulmonary rehabilitation conducted in ward settings

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Inability to self-complete the research questionnaires;

          -  Presence of the following issues at the time of the examination or in the medical
             data: disturbances of consciousness, psychotic symptoms or other serious psychiatric
             disorders

          -  Initiation of psychiatric treatment during the research project;

          -  Patient's refusal at any stage of the research project.
